---
title: "01 | Seeking"
author: "C.O."
date: "January 2026"
draft: false
---

When you are seeking something, it means that you go looking for it. As we start a new year, may we look for GOD in every area of our lives: whether it is for ways to improve physical health, financial issues, relationships, or spiritually. Seek HIM in all things.

Meditate on these verses to gain wisdom:

-   Week 1
    -   Deuteronomy 4:29
-   Week 2
    -   Luke 11:10
-   Week 3
    -   Psalms 105:3-4
-   Week 4
    -   Isaiah 55:6


